Mugabe Says Zimbabweans Must Hold Majority Mine Stakes, DPA Says

-- B y   A n t o n y   S g u a z z i n
-- 
2011-03-28T06:02:51Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-28/mugabe-says-zimbabweans-to-hold-majority-stakes-in-mine-projects-dpa-says.html
Zimbabwe will only work with
international mining companies if they are willing to be
minority shareholders in projects, President Robert Mugabe said,
according to Deutsche Presse Agentur.  Anglo American Plc (AAL)  and  Rio Tinto Plc (RIO)  need to transform
their operation in the country, Mugabe said, according to DPA.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net  